              <span>✓ Mac & Windows password recovery</span>
              <span>✓ Performance optimization</span>
              <span>✓ Professional software configuration</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card premium">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <rect x="3" y="3" width="8" height="8"/>
                <rect x="13" y="3" width="8" height="8"/>
                <rect x="3" y="13" width="8" height="8"/>
                <rect x="13" y="13" width="8" height="8"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Executive Windows Solutions</h3>
            <p>Specialized Windows 11 Pro optimization, Microsoft Office 365 enterprise setup, and business application integration for Southlake professionals.</p>
            <div class="service-features">
              <span>✓ Windows 11 Pro optimization</span>
              <span>✓ Office 365 enterprise setup</span>
              <span>✓ Business application integration</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card premium">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="m16 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1Z"/>
                <path d="m2 16 3-8 3 8c-.87.65-1.92 1-3 1s-2.13-.35-3-1Z"/>
