            <p>Complete smart home computer integration and network security. Protect your luxury automation systems and ensure seamless connectivity throughout your estate.</p>
            <div class="service-features">
              <span>✓ Smart home network security</span>
              <span>✓ Automation system integration</span>
              <span>✓ Estate-wide WiFi optimization</span>
