        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Southlake Specific -->
    <section class="location-focus">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Why Southlake's Elite Choose GadgetFix</h2>
        <div class="location-grid">
          <div class="location-feature">
            <h3>Luxury Home Service</h3>
            <p>From Timarron to Waterstone, we provide the level of service that matches your lifestyle. Protective coverings, clean workspace setup, and utmost respect for your luxury home environment.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="location-feature">
            <h3>Executive Scheduling</h3>
            <p>Flexible scheduling around your business commitments. Early morning, evening, and weekend appointments. Same-day emergency service for critical business needs.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="location-feature">
            <h3>Business Owner Support</h3>
            <p>Special services for Southlake entrepreneurs and executives. Multi-device management, home office optimization, and business continuity planning.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="location-feature">
            <h3>Privacy & Discretion</h3>
            <p>Complete confidentiality and professional discretion. Our vetted technicians understand the importance of privacy for high-profile Southlake residents.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Southlake Lifestyle -->
    <section class="lifestyle-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Computer Service That Matches Your Lifestyle</h2>
        <div class="lifestyle-grid">
          <div class="lifestyle-item">
            <h3>Country Club Professional</h3>
            <p>Emergency computer service during important business meetings at Timarron Country Club or while entertaining clients at home.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="lifestyle-item">
            <h3>Corporate Executive</h3>
            <p>Home office optimization for Fortune 500 executives. Secure remote access setup and business-grade network security.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="lifestyle-item">
            <h3>Entrepreneur</h3>
            <p>Multi-device management for business owners. Seamless synchronization between home office, mobile devices, and cloud systems.</p>
          </div>
          
